<br>
I've been messing with different classes on different servers:<br>
<br>
lvl 5 Albion wizard<br>
lvl 5 Albion Infiltrator<br>
lvl 5 Hibernia Eldritch<br>
lvl 5 Midgard Berzerker<br>
<br>
and a bunch of lvl 3 and 4's that I may play to 5 to choose a class and evaluate.<br>
<br>
In EQ I've played a Bard to 55, Monk to 47 and necro to 51...Bard is fun to run around with and quest, but Monk is a blast all around...so I was looking for something similar in DAOC.<br>
<br>
So far the berzerker is as close as I've gotten. A purely offensive, light armor wearing, duel axe wielding buzz saw. Once I trained him at 5, threw a bronze double bladed axe in one hand and my &quot;guild&quot; axe in the other - I was destroying yellows solo.<br>
<br>
<br>
thanks in advance!<br>
